episodes.title: Unexplained Possibilities Podcast w/ fomer scientologist Torymagoo44
episodes.description: Join Melvin and guest, former Scientologist Tory Christman , as she tells some of the secrets Scientology doesn't want you to know and her experiences with this cult like organization masquerading as a religion. Tory also goes into detail with how brainwashing works and gives out great advice to our listeners. Tory was in Scientology for 30 years and before making her great escape in 2000. To hear more of Tory's experiences please check out her youtube channel!  Tory's Youtube Channel https://www.youtube.com/user/ToryMago...  Tory's escape https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6cMPP...  http://www.xenu.net/  Mike Rinders Blog https://www.mikerindersblog.org  Don't forget to follow Unexplained on Facebook and Twitter   Facebook https://www.facebook.com/unexplainedp...  Twitter https://twitter.com/Unexpl_Podcast
